cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with visual place recognition, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves depth estimation, which is a common topic in robotics, making cs.RO (Robotics) a likely category as well. The paper uses machine learning techniques to improve recognition performance, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves developing a new system, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper evaluates its system on a benchmark dataset, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.MM (Multimedia).
